		<h2>About</h2>

		<h3> Thassos Island </h3>

		<p>Thassos Island - according to Homer Emerald Siren Island, the greenest island in the Aegean Sea, population of about 30,000 people, two hospitals, more than 70 beaches, two ports, 8 marinas, hundreds of restaurants, cafes and shops.</p>

