			<li>Airport Kavala 15 km,</li>
			<li>Thessaloniki Airport 190 km.</li>
			<li>The administrative center of Kavala is 30 km away.</li>
		</ul>

		<h3> Home </h3>

		<div class="info_list">
			<div class="info_item">
				<div class="info_item__number">220m<sup>2</sup></div>
