				<div class="info_item__number">65m</div>
				<div class="info_item__content">above the sea</div>
			</div>

			<div class="info_item">
				<div class="info_item__number">Sea view</div>
				<div class="info_item__content">to the sunset</div>
			</div>
		</div>

		<p>
			House of 220 square meters located on a plot of 2400 square meters. House 780 meters from the sea, on a hill 65 meters above sea level, panoramic sea views, views of the sunset and Mount Athos. Architect it. (D. Giovanelli).
		</p>

		<p>
			The house is in natural stone (granite), made by hereditary masons, completely athermal German glazing, internal doors are stainless steel + glass. inside natural stone (dolomite) and marble plaster without drywall. Ceilings - marble plaster without plasterboard with integrated designer lighting. Dolomite ladder 3 cm.
		</p>

		<p>
			The floors are stone (dolomite 2 cm) with heating, 1st floor and s / nodes, wall cladding - dolomite 1 cm × 30 cm × 60 cm, cornices and plinth are massive dolomite.
		</p>

		<p>
			2nd floor wood parquet. The climate is separate water (Viessmann thermal pump).
		</p>

		<ol>
			<li>Fireroom with panoramic sea views,</li>
			<li>master bedroom with panoramic sea views and private bathroom.</li>
			<li>A guest studio with a separate entrance, panoramic sea views and a private bathroom</li>
			<li>Children's bedroom.</li>
			<li>Study or bedroom.</li>
			<li>Sauna / hammam</li>
			<li>Cold Wine Room</li>
			<li>Dining room / kitchen with panoramic sea views and access to the pool, solarium</li>
			<li>4 bathrooms, all in natural stone (dolomite)</li>
		</ol>

		<p>
			All GROHE sanitary ware is integrated into the walls.
		</p>

		<p>
			Construction is strictly according to the project with the approval and documentation of intermediate stages (lightning protection, floors, bearing supports, earthquake-resistant foundation (A-klasse).
		</p>

		<p>
			All stages of construction are also photographed.
		</p>

		<p>
			Plot 24 ares, pool 44 sq.m, heated, light, integrated with a jacuzzi. Palms, fruiting olives, avocados, citrus fruits, paving stones. Video surveillance, security, optical internet cable, water supply, sewerage, electricity 3 phases 35 kw. Installation of a solar power plant up to 15 kvh is possible.
		</p>

		<p>
			Completion 90%. I sell fully completed with all life support systems, without furniture. Possibility of installing furniture, organizing room service, gardener, renting. Within walking distance of 5 beaches (3 sandy with cafes, sun loungers and umbrellas, 2 wild ones), a large marina "Limenaria" 5 km from the house, rental, yacht and boat service), shops, a pharmacy, a cafe within walking distance. (10-15 min walk).
		</p>

		<p>
			Nearby I am building absolutely the same house for myself. I guarantee the quality, it's not a shame to be a neighbor)))
		</p>

		<p>
			Turnkey price without furniture € 720'000
		</p>

		<p>
			The deposit is 50% and in 3 months everything will be ready.
		</p>

